{"tid":402113,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩出來做野,買幾多危疾醫療保險好？","createTime":"2017-09-16T07:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T10:07:42.000Z","uid":82040,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b67b3bf387a075e1fe950d08e6bb1087c9a1643d","tid":402113,"uid":82040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:25:42.000Z","msg":"23歲女，無煙無酒，身體健康，<br />\n<br />\n相信我父母已幫我買了人壽，咁 買幾多危疾醫療保險好？<br />\n<br />\n我暫時做緊政府contract 位，睇公立醫院免費，所以睇私人醫生跌打 無得claim<br />\n<br />\n有保險fd suggest 我如果買only一份就買危疾先，因為愈後生買愈平。<br />\n佢draft左份100萬保額，sunlife, 年供$17000, 供25年<br />\n<br />\n我屋企人就覺得 買7-80萬保額已經夠，佢suggest我 買 賠一百萬的危疾，而我歲數要 月供$1500左右，會否太高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋我覺得佢好似有些chur我係咁買，買埋投資 儲蓄 榨埋我有剩既一萬蚊人工咁<br />\n佢咁chur 但張單又ok ge 好無照買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af2247ac42ea5756b6aeb900dfcd14309f3a9e9","tid":402113,"uid":82040,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/152639_77acc2e83ff128307943cd07b085cb0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F152639_77acc2e83ff128307943cd07b085cb0d.jpg&h=96bfd13a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/152640_6a727f29d1a3a03e8d671cb32f3d0b27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F152640_6a727f29d1a3a03e8d671cb32f3d0b27.jpg&h=67e1c1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/152641_ad99125a824881a3acd64d12d8c6f089.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F152641_ad99125a824881a3acd64d12d8c6f089.jpg